        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Data-Driven Foster Parent Recruitment and Retention Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires state plans for child welfare services to provide for the development and implementation of a family partnership plan to improve foster care placement stability, increase rates of kinship placements, and align the racial and ethnic composition of foster and adoptive families with that of children in need of homes.</p>]]>
        </text>
